<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0c8a3bd1-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80r–1"><num value="80r–1">§ 80r–1.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this subchapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id0c8a3bd2-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80r–1/1"><num value="1" class="bold">(1)</num><heading class="bold"> Board of Regents</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Board of Regents” means the Board of Regents of the Smithsonian Institution.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id0c8a3bd3-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80r–1/2"><num value="2" class="bold">(2)</num><heading class="bold"> Council</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Council” means the National Museum of African American History and Culture Council established by <ref href="/us/usc/t20/s80r–3">section 80r–3 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id0c8a3bd4-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80r–1/3"><num value="3" class="bold">(3)</num><heading class="bold"> Museum</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Museum” means the National Museum of African American History and Culture established by <ref href="/us/usc/t20/s80r–2">section 80r–2 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id0c8a3bd5-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795" identifier="/us/usc/t20/s80r–1/4"><num value="4" class="bold">(4)</num><heading class="bold"> Secretary</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Secretary” means the Secretary of the Smithsonian Institution.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id0c8a3bd6-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795">(<ref href="/us/pl/108/184/s3">Pub. L. 108–184, § 3</ref>, <date date="2003-12-16">Dec. 16, 2003</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/117/2676">117 Stat. 2676</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
